snippet.title: I Survived 100 Days in Better Minecraft PLUS Hardcore… Here’s What Happened
snippet.description:
I spent 100 Days In not just Better Minecraft... But Better Minecraft PLUS Hardcore.

In this video, I tried to beat Better Minecraft PLUS in 100 Days Hardcore.
This was not easy, this was quite difficult for me, as a matter of fact it was extremely difficult. Due to it being highly modded, and has about 90 more mods than Better Minecraft. These mods change pretty much everything in the game including mobs, terrain, landscape, dimensions, atmosphere, and bosses. Now let's beat Better Minecraft Plus...

Time Stamps:
0:00 - intro
1:30 - 1-10
9:42 - 10-30
19:42 - 30-40
27:40 - 40-60
36:20 - 60-90
46:16 - 90-99
53:38 - 100

This video took over 40 hours to complete in total, you have no clue how thankful I would be if you'd just push the subscribe button, Notification bell, and like the video. Thank you for everything that you have done :)

Better Minecraft Plus Modpack:
https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/better-minecraft-plus 

This Video was inspired by Luke The Notable, Forge Labs, and Suev
